04:26.684 --> 04:28.686
Do you understand?
ALL: Yes, sir!

04:28.770 --> 04:31.356
(ROCK MUSIC PLAYING)

04:33.274 --> 04:35.401
FEMALE MARINE:
Right now, right now.

04:37.362 --> 04:40.239
