04:58.883 --> 05:00.069
FEMALE MARINE:
Get off my wall.

05:00.093 --> 05:01.177
I can make it!

05:01.260 --> 05:03.429
Get off my rope and
get to the back of the line.

05:08.601 --> 05:10.329
