Get those arms straight, Leavey!

05:10.353 --> 05:11.729
Get those arms straight!

05:11.896 --> 05:13.147
I want straight arms!

05:13.231 --> 05:15.441
You're gonna die out there,
you hear me?

05:16.025 --> 05:18.861
Have fun at the graduation.
You're a failure. (SPITS)

05:19.237 --> 05:20.446
