10:58.909 --> 11:00.161
Yes, Master Sergeant.

11:04.540 --> 11:06.959
One more hiccup and I'll see
you kicked out of here,

11:07.043 --> 11:08.919
do you copy me?
Yes, Master Sergeant.

11:09.712 --> 11:11.422
All right, you're on EMI,
shit detail,

11:11.505 --> 11:13.174
